                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, and live in London-street. The prisoner pawned these sheets with me about seven o'clock on the evening of the 24th of June, in the name of John Brown—he said his mother sent him with them—I lent him 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. on them.</p>
